OL,5,ETO ALL INTELLIGENT 'ZINERSS/--&Q+'S.+.+
OL,6,E(about two and counting..)             
OL,7,BAren't some the things people say      
OL,8,Bfunny? A few days back one of my       
OL,9,Bfriends said that he had tried to pick 
OL,10,Bup a girl and failed. This made me     
OL,11,Bwonder. Had the girl fallen over and,  
OL,12,Bif so, was it an accident or was she   
OL,13,Bpushed? I then considered that my      
OL,14,Bfriend had decided to check her weight 
OL,15,Bfor her free of charge. I told him he  
OL,16,Bwas wasting his time and should try    
OL,17,Bpicking up dumb-bells instead so that  
OL,18,Bhe would get muscles and attract girls!
OL,19,EFlimbo, the talking electric meter     
