OL,5,EDEAR 'ZINERS              S/--&Q+'S.+.+
OL,7,BI'm depressed. Can anyone answer me    
OL,8,Bthis question?                         
OL,10,BWhat exactly is love? Throughout my 17 
OL,11,Byears on this planet I have never met  
OL,12,Banyone who I could honestly say I      
OL,13,Bfelt love for. I am even thinking of   
OL,14,Basking a girl out just because I don't 
OL,15,Bwant to be the only one not dating!    
OL,16,BDoes love happen or do you have to ask 
OL,17,Bsomeone out and then it happens after a
OL,18,Bwhile? Am I just meant to always be    
OL,19,Balone?E  The Lunchbox                  
