OL,5,EREAL LIFE STORIES         S/--&Q+'S.+.+
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BWe're after more of your real-life     
OL,8,Bstories to feature on Club.            
OL,9,B                                       
OL,10,BThe subject is:EYour quest for fame.B  
OL,11,BHave you ever formed a band and sent   
OL,12,Boff a demo to a record company? Have   
OL,13,Byou ever tried to appear on a TV show? 
OL,14,BWhat were your experiences in your     
OL,15,Bquest for bright lights. Maybe you're  
OL,16,Bfamous already eh?                     
OL,18,BWrite to us, remembering to include    
OL,19,Byour full name, age and address.       
